    # Suffix-stripping heuristics (left here as documentation of the approach
    # that was REPLACED by the explicit mapping below).
    # These suffix rules turn adjective → country name but produce too many
    # false positives (e.g., "Mexican" → "Mexica") to be relied upon alone.
    # They are kept here as comments so future maintainers understand why an
    # explicit mapping was chosen instead.
